@@TJvDirMask
Description:
This set is the set of options for the TJvDirectorySpy. 

* dmFileNameChange : Spy for file name changes. 
* dmDirnameChange : Spy for directory name changes. 
* dmAttributesChange : Spy for file/directory attributes changes. 
* dmSizeChange : Spy for file size changes. 
* dmLastWriteChange : Spy for file last write attributes (file modifications). 
* dmSecurityChange : Spy for file/directory security changes. (ONLY UNDER WINDOWS NT !!!)

